OL,3,CCriminal investigation after pensioner
OL,4,Cfell ill in police custody
OL,6,FAn investigation has been launched by
OL,7,Fthe Independent Office for Police
OL,8,FConduct (IOPC) after a man became
OL,9,Fseriously unwell while in police
OL,10,Fcustody.
OL,12,FThe 80-year-old man was taken into
OL,13,Fcustody by Cheshire Constabulary after
OL,14,Fbeing arrested for suspected drink-
OL,15,Fdriving close to midnight on 7
OL,16,FDecember 2025.
