OL,3,CCriminal investigation after pensioner
OL,4,Cfell ill in police custody
OL,6,FWhile in police custody, staff carried
OL,7,Fout regular welfare checks, and at
OL,8,Faround 6 am on 8 December, it was
OL,9,Freported that he appeared to be having
OL,10,Fa seizure.
OL,12,FThe pensioner was taken to the
OL,13,Fhospital, where it was determined he
OL,14,Fhad had a stroke. It is unclear
OL,15,Fwhether this occurred before or after
OL,16,Fthe man was arrested.
