OL,3,CCriminal investigation after pensioner
OL,4,Cfell ill in police custody
OL,6,FConcerns were raised about the use of
OL,7,Fforce during a cell check at around
OL,8,F4.30am. A police officer is now under
OL,9,Finvestigation for assault, as well as
OL,10,Fgross misconduct.
OL,12,FIOPC Director Amanda Rowe said: "In
OL,13,Flight of the seriousness of the man's
OL,14,Fcondition, it is important for the
OL,15,Fcircumstances of his arrest and
OL,16,Fdetention to be independently
OL,17,Finvestigated.
