OL,3,CCriminal investigation after pensioner
OL,4,Cfell ill in police custody
OL,6,F"While it is not clear whether the
OL,7,Fpolice use of force may have
OL,8,Fcontributed to the man's condition
OL,9,Fdeteriorating, evidence gathered so
OL,10,Ffar indicates a criminal offence may
OL,11,Fhave been committed.
OL,13,F"The serving of notices does not mean
OL,14,Fthat criminal or disciplinary
OL,15,Fproceedings will necessarily follow.
OL,16,FOn conclusion of our investigation, we
OL,17,Fwill decide whether to refer the case
OL,18,Fto the Crown Prosecution Service, or
OL,19,Fwhether misconduct proceedings are
OL,20,Fappropriate."
