OL,3,CCriminal investigation after pensioner
OL,4,Cfell ill in police custody
OL,6,FThe IOPC investigation will focus on
OL,7,Fthe decision-making and actions of the
OL,8,Fpolice involved in the man's arrest
OL,9,Fand subsequent detention. This will
OL,10,Finclude the level of care and support
OL,11,Fprovided while in custody.
